# ================================
# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT CHECKLIST
# ================================
# Before deploying to production:
# 1. Generate a new JWT_SECRET (64+ char random string)
# 2. Update FRONTEND_URL to your production domain
# 3. Update API_BASE_URL to your production n8n instance
# 4. Update GOOGLE_SHEET_ID with your production sheet
# 5. Update all SHEET_GID values
# 6. REMOVE test credentials from authController.js
# 7. REMOVE admin bypass from AdminLoginPage.js
# 8. Set NODE_ENV=production
# 9. Never commit .env files to version control
# 10. Use environment variable management (Vercel, Railway, etc.)
# ================================

# ================================
# WEBHOOK ENDPOINTS (n8n)
# ================================
# Your n8n webhook should handle these endpoints:
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/capture-lead
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/simulate-payment  
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/contact-form
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/ai-chat
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/auth/register
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/auth/login
# - ${API_BASE_URL}/admin-auth

# Admin Authentication Webhook (for JWT validation)
ADMIN_AUTH_WEBHOOK_URL=${API_BASE_URL}/admin-auth
